computeTypeName.description: Compute type. For more information, see [Amazon WorkSpaces Bundles](http://aws.amazon.com/workspaces/details/#Amazon_WorkSpaces_Bundles). Valid values are `VALUE`, `STANDARD`, `PERFORMANCE`, `POWER`, `GRAPHICS`, `POWERPRO` and `GRAPHICSPRO`.

runningMode.description: Running mode. For more information, see [Manage the WorkSpace Running Mode](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/workspaces/latest/adminguide/running-mode.html). Valid values are `AUTO_STOP` and `ALWAYS_ON`.

runningModeAutoStopTimeoutInMinutes.description: Time after a user logs off when WorkSpaces are automatically stopped. Configured in 60-minute intervals.
